fields.name: AppInsightsAgentVersions
fields.description: Indicates the versions of application insight agent

fields.name: AppInsightsInstrumentationKey
fields.description: Target application insight instrumentation key, null or whitespace include empty will disable monitoringSettings

fields.name: AppInsightsSamplingRate
fields.description: Indicates the sampling rate of application insight agent, should be in range [0.0, 100.0]

fields.name: Error
fields.description: Error when apply Monitoring Setting changes.

fields.name: TraceEnabled
fields.description: Indicates whether enable the trace functionality, which will be deprecated since api version 2020-11-01-preview. Please leverage appInsightsInstrumentationKey to indicate if monitoringSettings enabled or not
